To redeem your $10 promotional certificate, simply:
1. Go to the Amazon.com Electronics, Software, Computers, Camera &
Photo, or Cell Phones & Service stores.
2. Select the items you want (totaling $99 or more, excluding shipping
and tax) and add them to your Shopping Cart.
3. Click the "Proceed to checkout" button (sorry, customers cannot
redeem their promotional certificate using our 1-Click service).
You'll be taken to the checkout page, where you can review your order
and select shipping options.
4. Enter your promotional claim code in the space provided in the
right column (located below your order total) and click the Apply
button. The certificate will be redeemed and the page will refresh
with your revised order total. Please note that you must pay for any
remaining order balance with a credit card.
5. Click the "Place your order" button. You're done! If you want to
review the details of your order again, click the Your Account button
in the upper right corner of the page.

